        <node TEXT="sjw，新股业绩不及预期，一季度亏200万。昨天-5，今天跌停开，给我看傻了。加了3层，没做T，还亏-6，千万别往下杀啊。我是傻逼，之前早该走的。以后要注意了" ID="0pX6pZKHaT" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3Esjw%EF%BC%8C%E6%96%B0%E8%82%A1%E4%B8%9A%E7%BB%A9%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8A%E9%A2%84%E6%9C%9F%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E4%BA%8F200%E4%B8%87%E3%80%82%E6%98%A8%E5%A4%A9-5%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E8%B7%8C%E5%81%9C%E5%BC%80%EF%BC%8C%E7%BB%99%E6%88%91%E7%9C%8B%E5%82%BB%E4%BA%86%E3%80%82%E5%8A%A0%E4%BA%863%E5%B1%82%EF%BC%8C%E6%B2%A1%E5%81%9AT%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%98%E4%BA%8F-6%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E5%88%AB%E5%BE%80%E4%B8%8B%E6%9D%80%E5%95%8A%E3%80%82%E6%88%91%E6%98%AF%E5%82%BB%E9%80%BC%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E6%97%A9%E8%AF%A5%E8%B5%B0%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82%E4%BB%A5%E5%90%8E%E8%A6%81%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E4%BA%86%3C/span%3E" STYLE="fork"/>
