        <node TEXT="今天大盘高潮了。收3088，这个箱体就要突破，很好的形态。深创科都大涨，232，无敌" ID="U086RazEeV" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E5%A4%A7%E7%9B%98%E9%AB%98%E6%BD%AE%E4%BA%86%E3%80%82%E6%94%B63088%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E7%AE%B1%E4%BD%93%E5%B0%B1%E8%A6%81%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%BE%88%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84%E5%BD%A2%E6%80%81%E3%80%82%E6%B7%B1%E5%88%9B%E7%A7%91%E9%83%BD%E5%A4%A7%E6%B6%A8%EF%BC%8C232%EF%BC%8C%E6%97%A0%E6%95%8C%3C/span%3E" STYLE="fork"/>
        <node TEXT="上涨最主要的动力：北向资金。北向为什么要买？日元贬值，贬值太快了，导致资产缩水非常严重，而且是全面的缩水，资金外流，显示港股，表现为上周五连阳，周线9p，太强了。A股是滞后的，今天资金才大举进入。净流入230。 这个流入不会是一天的，随着日元继续下跌，资金会不断进入，这里应该是一个做多的节点。 周四爱在冰川就说过这里港股会反推A股，就是说的北向。" ID="hXQEZjMtPM" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E4%B8%8A%E6%B6%A8%E6%9C%80%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%9A%E5%8C%97%E5%90%91%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91%E3%80%82%E5%8C%97%E5%90%91%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E8%A6%81%E4%B9%B0%EF%BC%9F%E6%97%A5%E5%85%83%E8%B4%AC%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%8C%E8%B4%AC%E5%80%BC%E5%A4%AA%E5%BF%AB%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E8%B5%84%E4%BA%A7%E7%BC%A9%E6%B0%B4%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E4%B8%A5%E9%87%8D%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E4%B8%94%E6%98%AF%E5%85%A8%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E7%BC%A9%E6%B0%B4%EF%BC%8C%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91%E5%A4%96%E6%B5%81%EF%BC%8C%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%EF%BC%8C%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%8A%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E8%BF%9E%E9%98%B3%EF%BC%8C%E5%91%A8%E7%BA%BF9p%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%AA%E5%BC%BA%E4%BA%86%E3%80%82A%E8%82%A1%E6%98%AF%E6%BB%9E%E5%90%8E%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91%E6%89%8D%E5%A4%A7%E4%B8%BE%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%E3%80%82%E5%87%80%E6%B5%81%E5%85%A5230%E3%80%82%20%E8%BF%99%E4%B8%AA%E6%B5%81%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E9%9A%8F%E7%9D%80%E6%97%A5%E5%85%83%E7%BB%A7%E7%BB%AD%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C%EF%BC%8C%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%AD%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%81%9A%E5%A4%9A%E7%9A%84%E8%8A%82%E7%82%B9%E3%80%82%20%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E7%88%B1%E5%9C%A8%E5%86%B0%E5%B7%9D%E5%B0%B1%E8%AF%B4%E8%BF%87%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%8D%E6%8E%A8A%E8%82%A1%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E8%AF%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%97%E5%90%91%E3%80%82%3C/span%3E" STYLE="fork"/>
