          <node TEXT="如洋神说，这里的容量切换了，宗申动力高开快速上板，成为容量载体。中信海直也被带起来，但是尾盘回落严重。万丰奥威也是冲高收绿，主力大幅流出。  中衡设计尾盘炸收0轴，宗申动力也被带开了，中信海直的大幅回落，等等都说明资金开始从低空切出去了，切到哪里？证券？不管怎么样，低空这里要调整的，参与的性价比不高了" ID="Opqxgzg6rE" _mubu_text="%3Cspan%3E%E5%A6%82%E6%B4%8B%E7%A5%9E%E8%AF%B4%EF%BC%8C%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%97%E7%94%B3%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%E9%AB%98%E5%BC%80%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E4%B8%8A%E6%9D%BF%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%B9%E9%87%8F%E8%BD%BD%E4%BD%93%E3%80%82%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%A1%E6%B5%B7%E7%9B%B4%E4%B9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E5%B8%A6%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E5%B0%BE%E7%9B%98%E5%9B%9E%E8%90%BD%E4%B8%A5%E9%87%8D%E3%80%82%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%B0%E5%A5%A5%E5%A8%81%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%86%B2%E9%AB%98%E6%94%B6%E7%BB%BF%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%BB%E5%8A%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E6%B5%81%E5%87%BA%E3%80%82%20%20%E4%B8%AD%E8%A1%A1%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%B0%BE%E7%9B%98%E7%82%B8%E6%94%B60%E8%BD%B4%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%97%E7%94%B3%E5%8A%A8%E5%8A%9B%E4%B9%9F%E8%A2%AB%E5%B8%A6%E5%BC%80%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%AD%E4%BF%A1%E6%B5%B7%E7%9B%B4%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E5%9B%9E%E8%90%BD%EF%BC%8C%E7%AD%89%E7%AD%89%E9%83%BD%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E8%B5%84%E9%87%91%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E4%BB%8E%E4%BD%8E%E7%A9%BA%E5%88%87%E5%87%BA%E5%8E%BB%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%87%E5%88%B0%E5%93%AA%E9%87%8C%EF%BC%9F%E8%AF%81%E5%88%B8%EF%BC%9F%E4%B8%8D%E7%AE%A1%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E6%A0%B7%EF%BC%8C%E4%BD%8E%E7%A9%BA%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E8%A6%81%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4%E7%9A%84%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8E%E7%9A%84%E6%80%A7%E4%BB%B7%E6%AF%94%E4%B8%8D%E9%AB%98%E4%BA%86%3C/span%3E" STYLE="fork"/>
